// THIS page the same way the markdown gallery above documents itself: every prose block below
// quotes or closely follows that file's own header comments (the canvas contract, the gate
// tiers), and the two examples at the end are REAL `Diagram` compositions (`VectorCanvasExample
// Diagram`/`VectorHoverExampleDiagram` below) read straight into an actual SVG file
